ess p\u00e5 Regjeringen for \u00e5 f\u00e5 innf\u00f8rt halv p-avgift s\u00e5 raskt som mulig. M\u00e5 ogs\u00e5 elbiler betale i bomringen, frykter Langolf at salget av elbiler vil g\u00e5 dramatisk ned. 18 prosent av medlemmene i elbilforeningen svarer i en unders\u00f8kelse at de kj\u00f8pte elbil fordi det er gratis \u00e5 parkere."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "bfeb9cb9ff282dc89c1b398ebf3cf33886363ebf465570d0fd16dd56a5b6c950"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T16:44:42.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Til alle som m\u00e5tte ha v\u00e6rt i tvil; fra nytt\u00e5r m\u00e5 ogs\u00e5 elbiler betale full parkeringsavgift i Trondheim."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/nyheter/article13974967.ece/39i6vi/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ElbilParkering06.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/eeb861e73bdc9cb0e94f640f247885057e1c82ac.jpg?598db4cc"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Elbiler m\u00e5 betale full p-avgift i Trondheim fra nytt\u00e5r -adressa.no", "Statsbudsjettet forvirrer", "Opp til hver kommune", "M\u00e5 reservere 80 plasser", "Lettere \u00e5 f\u00e5 parkert", "Skuffede elbileiere"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "eeb861e73bdc9cb0e94f640f247885057e1c82ac"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Trondheim parkering", "Norsk elbilforening", "parkeringsavgift", "Elbil"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Trondheim parkering,Norsk elbilforening,parkeringsavgift,Elbil"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "nyheter"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "automotive"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["betale full", "parkert", "elbiler st\u00e5 gratis", "betale", "halv pris", "betale full p-avgift", "elbil"]}, {"field": "kw-en